    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1931-11-27T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1931-11-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="155"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d155">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">462.00R296/5326</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Finnish Minister</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Aström</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-11-27">November 27,
                            1931</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Excellency</hi>: I have the honor to refer to Your
                    Excellency’s note, dated October 27 [<hi rend="italic">24</hi>], 1931, by which
                    you were good enough to inform me about the proposal set forth by the President
                    of the United States in his statement of June 20, 1931, concerning the
                    postponement of payments upon the debts of foreign governments to the American
                    government during the fiscal year beginning July 1, 1931.</p>
                <p>I have the honor to inform Your Excellency that my Government has now instructed
                    me to state that it is glad to accept the proposal made by the President of the
                    United States, referred to above.</p>
                <p>Accept [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">L. Aström</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
